Cure Light Wounds
Discworld ritual help
Cure Light Wounds

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Cure light wounds -- Heals only the lightest of wounds.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Cure light wounds can be performed on a person or on yourself.  It gives you 
back a slight number of hit points and is the easiest of the 
curing rituals.  The success of this ritual is based on your 
faith.rituals.curing skill
.EP